1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:35,195
=Episode 25=
(May spring grow for the people where I fall.)

3
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:09,020
It really works.

4
00:01:10,980 --> 00:01:12,380
Don't just stand there.

5
00:01:12,860 --> 00:01:13,939
Collect his blood.

6
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:14,780
Yes.

7
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:19,780
Helian Shu, how dare you?

8
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:33,060
Zhao.

9
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,580
Helian Shu.

10
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:02,780
This must be Ning's skirt dagger.

11
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:04,300
Shut up.

12
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:06,580
You're not worthy to speak of my mother.

13
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:10,780
Since young,

14
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:13,739
my father bowed in submission.

15
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:14,940
Ning only had eyes

16
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:17,780
for that emperor lover of hers.

17
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:19,259
This nation

18
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:21,580
should have belonged to the family.

19
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:23,819
Anyone who doesn't help Helian Clan
fight for the throne

20
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:25,140
deserves to die.

21
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:27,500
So

22
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:32,300
you killed

23
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:34,580
Grandfather and Mother.

24
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:38,220
Who else?

25
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:26,139
My dear niece,

26
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:28,020
you can't kill me.

27
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:31,620
I've consumed an immortal's flesh

28
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:33,020
and become a flower slave.

29
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:36,260
I'm immortal and indestructible.

30
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:40,340
What can you do about it?

31
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,300
Father,

32
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,580
do you see that?

33
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:49,980
I killed the emperor and empress

34
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,700
and destroyed that lofty immortal.

35
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:54,260
One day,

36
00:03:55,020 --> 00:03:57,300
I can seize the Ning throne!

37
00:04:04,020 --> 00:04:05,420
Like you're worthy of that.

38
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:08,140
You won't be leaving today.

39
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:14,180
As expected of Ning's daughter.

40
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:17,020
So wicked.

41
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,820
But...

42
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:23,300
I've stationed my shadow guards
outside the city.

43
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:26,620
If I don't return before sunset,

44
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:30,419
they'll spread Verdant Decay
all across the country.

45
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:31,180
Why you!

46
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,340
Well?

47
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,900
As the future empress of Ning,

48
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:41,300
will you take personal revenge

49
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,820
or...

50
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,740
save your people?

51
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,100
Your Highness,

52
00:04:58,420 --> 00:04:59,579
I will have Pei Army

53
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:00,900
surround the capital.

54
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:02,660
Not even a fly can get out.

55
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:13,980
Get lost!

56
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:20,540
You made a wise choice,

57
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:27,220
my dear niece.

58
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,100
Immortal!

59
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:42,340
It worked!

60
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:43,540
Immortal!

61
00:05:44,660 --> 00:05:45,540
Immortal...

62
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:52,980
The duke has been

63
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,980
making big moves these days.

64
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,780
It's all thanks to your guidance

65
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:58,580
that the plan could go well.

66
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:01,420
Now I am an immortal,

67
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:04,300
but my army of flower slaves
isn't gathered yet.

68
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:05,460
Immortal,

69
00:06:05,780 --> 00:06:06,980
what should

70
00:06:07,540 --> 00:06:08,659
we do next?

71
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:11,259
You won't spread Verdant Decay
across Ning State

72
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:13,100
and can't bear to harm the people.

73
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:15,540
So what we can do now

74
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,139
is to wait.

75
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:17,860
Wait?

76
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:19,860
For what?

77
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,580
For human cruelty.

78
00:06:24,420 --> 00:06:26,340
For human selfishness.

79
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:30,020
For human greed.

80
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:46,780
General,

81
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,899
someone killed the guard last night.

82
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:50,140
The civilians escaped.

83
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,220
How many got out?

84
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:55,100
Still counting.

85
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:03,660
(Mother,)

86
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:08,220
(I'm so tired.)

87
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:10,779
Mother!

88
00:07:10,780 --> 00:07:11,540
Your Highness!

89
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:12,420
Your Highness.

90
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:27,220
(How could I fall asleep?)

91
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:29,540
(The people of Ning Capital need me.)

92
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:33,340
(Zhao,)

93
00:07:33,780 --> 00:07:36,540
(I won't let anyone harm you anymore.)

94
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,140
Mother,

95
00:07:58,780 --> 00:07:59,780
you're awake.

96
00:08:00,780 --> 00:08:04,139
I thought you and Father
were going to abandon me.

97
00:08:04,140 --> 00:08:05,460
Of course not.

98
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:07,780
I was just feeling weak.

99
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:09,580
I'm much better after some rest.

100
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:12,220
I'm sorry, Baobao.

101
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:14,980
I'm far worse compared

102
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:17,340
to my mother.

103
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:19,300
Nonsense!

104
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:22,100
You're the best mother in the world.

105
00:08:22,220 --> 00:08:24,740
The very, very best.

106
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:29,220
Don't cry.

107
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,540
I'm right here.

108
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:36,980
The flower slaves are missing,

109
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,460
and Helian Shu is planning something.

110
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:42,100
You must stay and guard your father.

111
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:43,740
Don't leave his side.

112
00:08:45,340 --> 00:08:46,660
If he wakes up,

113
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:52,100
tell him

114
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:53,980
that I love him.

115
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,660
Where are you going, Mother?

116
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:03,300
I'm going to treat the sick.

117
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,460
Have you forgotten?

118
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:15,820
I'm a physician.

119
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:18,460
Be good.

120
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:19,700
Alright?

121
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:28,620
Mother.

122
00:09:35,175 --> 00:09:39,695
(Baihua Hall)

123
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,180
Your Highness.

124
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,419
Where are you going?

125
00:09:42,420 --> 00:09:44,419
I just discovered a medicine

126
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:45,820
that works against Verdant Decay.

127
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:46,940
I'm going to gather it now.

128
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:49,019
Your Highness,
there's no need to go yourself.

129
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:50,340
I'll send someone.

130
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,139
You wouldn't recognize it.

131
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:53,059
I'll go myself.

132
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:54,340
I'll go with you then.

133
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:02,820
I saw...

134
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:05,539
I'm ordering you

135
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:06,580
to stay put.

136
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:07,820
No horse riding.

137
00:10:07,860 --> 00:10:08,980
Stay right here.

138
00:10:09,180 --> 00:10:09,980
But...

139
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:11,340
Are you disobeying me?

140
00:10:14,020 --> 00:10:14,860
Understood.

141
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,340
What are you doing?

142
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,620
You and I are one.

143
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,460
You know what I want.

144
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:51,380
Don't go.

145
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,539
You can't go!

146
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,820
You're sealed.

147
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:54,980
You can't stop me.

148
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:57,740
Have you thought this through?

149
00:10:58,380 --> 00:11:00,820
If you get that flower slave
to refine me,

150
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:02,500
you'll die too.

151
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:04,580
My life for an entire nation.

152
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:05,980
It's worth it.

153
00:11:06,380 --> 00:11:09,860
Leave those civilians unrelated to you

154
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:12,220
and go far away with Zhao.

155
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,980
Would a quiet life

156
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:16,500
be better?

157
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:17,700
I promise.

158
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:19,500
I'll never harm you both again.

159
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:20,499
I beg you.

160
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,419
I promise you.

161
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:23,500
Believe me. I'll keep my word.

162
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:24,980
I'm not like you.

163
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,860
I can't let others die

164
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:29,220
for my own survival.

165
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:31,620
I may someone I have,

166
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:33,180
but

167
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:35,740
I also have my duty.

168
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,100
I'm begging you.

169
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:40,940
Please.

170
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:42,139
I want to live.

171
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:43,379
I don't want to die!

172
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:45,259
I want to live!

173
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:46,499
I only wanted to live.

174
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:47,179
Please.

175
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,380
In the last life,

176
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:51,460
I failed to protect an entire village.

177
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,340
In this life,

178
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:56,100
I'll protect everyone in the nation.

179
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:58,700
Now get out of my body!

180
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:07,740
(Mother.)

181
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:08,980
(Father.)

182
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:10,340
(Zhao.)

183
00:12:11,140 --> 00:12:11,980
(Baobao.)

184
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:13,620
(Xiao.)

185
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:16,340
(We'll meet in the next life.)

186
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:22,980
You're here.

187
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:31,820
Back then,

188
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:34,500
if she had married me,

189
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:37,419
this dead end wouldn't exist today.

190
00:12:37,420 --> 00:12:38,580
Talking is pointless.

191
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:39,940
Lead the way.

192
00:12:41,180 --> 00:12:42,220
After you.

193
00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:45,780
(This is bad.
I must report to the general.)

194
00:12:54,175 --> 00:12:55,884
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

195
00:12:55,885 --> 00:12:58,734
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

196
00:12:58,735 --> 00:13:01,474
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

197
00:13:01,475 --> 00:13:03,104
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

198
00:13:03,105 --> 00:13:08,705
(Perhaps, if I reincarnate,)

199
00:13:08,755 --> 00:13:10,354
(I can rid myself of this demon heart.)

200
00:13:10,355 --> 00:13:13,114
(I will definitely
come back to find you.)

201
00:13:13,115 --> 00:13:15,964
(You must wait for me.)

202
00:13:15,965 --> 00:13:18,564
♪If in a dream♪

203
00:13:18,565 --> 00:13:23,354
♪I can hear your voice♪

204
00:13:23,355 --> 00:13:25,114
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

205
00:13:25,115 --> 00:13:27,765
♪Let it be us♪

206
00:13:27,985 --> 00:13:30,704
♪drawing endlessly close♪

207
00:13:30,705 --> 00:13:32,354
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

208
00:13:32,355 --> 00:13:38,014
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

209
00:13:38,015 --> 00:13:39,554
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

210
00:13:39,555 --> 00:13:42,304
♪Not even in time♪

211
00:13:42,305 --> 00:13:45,274
♪to tell you how I feel♪

212
00:13:45,275 --> 00:13:47,824
♪If the rain won't stop♪

213
00:13:47,825 --> 00:13:52,464
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

214
00:13:52,465 --> 00:13:55,074
♪Let love go on♪

215
00:13:55,075 --> 00:14:02,185
♪Until forever♪
